# Conductor Development TODO

**Project**: Lightweight async task queue for Python (PostgreSQL-backed, no Redis)  
**Version**: 0.1.0 MVP  
**Timeline**: ~6 weeks (6 sprints)  
**Last Updated**: 2025-01-15

---

