**Acceptance Criteria**:
- [ ] Retries execute after correct delays
- [ ] Failed tasks move to DLQ after max retries
- [ ] DLQ tasks can be manually retried
- [ ] Backoff strategies calculate correctly
- [ ] Retry logic has 85%+ test coverage

